{"lc": 1, "type": "constructor", "id": ["langchain", "schema", "document", "Document"], "kwargs": {"metadata": {"Header 1": "Problem 39:"}, "page_content": "## **Error Summary**  \n**Root Cause:** A **Nested Touchable Conflict**. The userInfo container in PostCard.tsx was a TouchableOpacity with flex: 1. This created a broad \"hit-box\" covering the entire top section of the card, hijacking clicks intended for the main post detail navigation.  \n## **Solution Summary**  \n**Fix:** De-classified the broad header wrapper by changing it to a standard View and applied targeted TouchableOpacity wrappers only to the **Avatar** and **Username**. Added e.stopPropagation() to the community link to prevent event bubbling to the main card.  \n## **Required Code Snippets**  \n#### **File: PostCard.tsx**  \n**1\\. Isolate Touch Targets in Header**  \nReplace the original userInfo block with specific touchable zones:  \nTypeScript  \n{/\\* 1. Changed wrapper from TouchableOpacity to View \\*/}  \n&lt;View style={styles.userInfo}&gt;  \n{/\\* 2. Isolated touch target for Avatar \\*/}  \n&lt;TouchableOpacity onPress={handleProfileNavigation}&gt;  \n{post?.user?.avatar_url ? (  \n&lt;Image source={{ uri: post.user.avatar_url }} style={styles.avatar} /&gt;  \n) : (  \n&lt;View style={styles.defaultAvatar}&gt;  \n&lt;Text style={styles.avatarText}&gt;  \n{pathOr('User', \\['user', 'name'\\], post)?.charAt(0)?.toUpperCase()}  \n&lt;/Text&gt;  \n&lt;/View&gt;  \n)}  \n&lt;/TouchableOpacity&gt;  \n&lt;View style={styles.userTextContainer}&gt;  \n&lt;View style={styles.communityRow}&gt;  \n<Text  \nonPress={(e) => {  \ne.stopPropagation(); // 3. Prevent triggering main card  \nhandleCommunityNavigation();  \n}}  \nstyle={styles.communityName}  \n\\>  \n{pathOr('', \\['community_name'\\], post) || pathOr('', \\['user', 'prefix'\\], post)}  \n&lt;/Text&gt;  \n&lt;/View&gt;  \n{/\\* 4. Isolated touch target for User Name \\*/}  \n&lt;TouchableOpacity onPress={handleProfileNavigation}&gt;  \n&lt;Text style={styles.userName} numberOfLines={1}&gt;  \n{pathOr('', \\['user', 'name'\\], post)}  \n&lt;/Text&gt;  \n&lt;/TouchableOpacity&gt;  \n&lt;/View&gt;  \n&lt;/View&gt;  \n**2\\. Main Card Navigation (Optional Logging)**  \nUpdate the root TouchableOpacity to verify navigation:  \nTypeScript  \n<TouchableOpacity  \nstyle={\\[styles.modernPostCard, ...\\]}  \nonPress={() => {  \nconsole.log('Post Detail Triggered for ID:', post.id);  \nhandlePostClick(post.id);  \n}}  \nactiveOpacity={0.8}  \n\\>  \n{/\\* Content \\*/}  \n&lt;/TouchableOpacity&gt;  \nWould you like me to help you adjust the spacing between these cards in the Feed.tsx list next?", "type": "Document"}}